<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Verify Your Email - Marka</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4f46e5; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: white; }
    .content { padding: 30px; background: #f8fafc; }
    .code { 
      font-size: 32px; 
      font-weight: bold; 
      text-align: center; 
      letter-spacing: 5px; 
      margin: 30px 0;
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Email Verification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with Marka. Please use the verification code below to complete your email verification:</p>

      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>

      <p>This code will expire in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes. If you didn't request this verification, please ignore this email.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The Marka Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{formatDate now}} Marka. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Uganda's Premier Report Card System</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>